data.description: This beautiful move-in ready home is in a highly sought-after area and has a pristine subdivision that is well kept. Home is located minutes away from The Georgia International Horse Park where the 1996 Centennial Olympic Games hosted mountain bike, and equestrian venues. Great and fun places to explore like Restaurants, Spas, Parks and many more are a treasure to have and here in this LOCATION you would find them all! This home is calling FIRST TIME HOME BUYERS and OTHERS into a space of Comfort and Peace! This is 4 bedrooms, 2 and half baths, and a beautiful back deck for great entertainments with family and friends! Home have been upgraded with LVT floors, kitchen, and freshly painted areas. Home comes with Stainless Steel stove, microwave, fridge and dishwasher that is great for everyday needs. Privately spacious back yard! This home is a must have!
